clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: Vosevi Voxilaprevir DB08934 DB11613 is approved for use in patients with genotypes 1 6 who have been previously treated with an NS5A inhibitor or patients with genotypes 1a or 3 infection who have previously been treated with an HCV regimen containing DB08934 without an NS5A inhibitor L935

contraindications.pharmacodynamics: Voxilaprevir is a direct acting antiviral agent that targets viral NS3 4A protein and causes a decrease in serum HCV RNA levels It disrupts HCV replication by specifically inhibiting the critical functions of NS3 4A protein in the replication complex It does not appear to prolong the QT interval even when given at 9 times the maximum recommended dose FDA Label
